    whyItMatters: 'UPI has revolutionized digital payments in India by making transactions instant, free (no merchant discount rates for most transactions), and accessible to anyone with a smartphone. It has brought over 300 million users into the digital payments ecosystem, many of whom had no prior access to card payments or net banking. UPI processed over 100 billion transactions worth $2+ trillion in 2023 alone. Its open architecture (built on the NPCI\'s unified platform) allows any bank or third-party app to participate, fostering fierce competition and innovation. UPI has become a blueprint for real-time payment systems worldwide, with countries like Singapore, UAE, and France adopting similar frameworks.',
