    whyItMatters: 'ChatGPT crossed 100 million users in just 2 months — the fastest-growing consumer application in history. It has transformed how people interact with AI, making advanced natural language understanding accessible to everyone. Businesses use it for customer service, content generation, code writing, and data analysis. It has triggered an arms race among tech giants (Google\'s Gemini, Meta\'s Llama, Anthropic\'s Claude) and catalyzed a $100 billion+ AI industry. For professionals, it is a productivity multiplier; for students, a personalized tutor; for developers, a coding assistant. Understanding how it works demystifies both its capabilities and its limitations.',
    formula: 'P(next_token | context) = softmax(attention(Q,K,V) × feed_forward) — where the model computes the probability of every possible next token given the entire conversation history, using attention mechanisms to weigh relevance.',
